page.title: 09HOUSING-DESCRIPTIONS
page.content: { 1.DETACHED BUNGALOW},BUILT{1960}OF {BRICK}WITH TYROLEAN FINISH,TILED ROOF. THREE BEDROOMS WITH RECENT EXTENSION FOR EXTRA BEDROOM.ATTACHED GARAGE AND CELLAR. { 2.TERRACED HOUSE,}BUILT{1898}OF {BRICK.}FRONTED WITH ORIGINAL VICTORIAN VERANDAH WHICH IS THE ENTRANCE TO THE MIDDLE LEVEL OF A SPLIT LEVEL HOUSE. LOWEST LEVEL,AT REAR,CONTAINS LIVING ROOM,SCULLERY,KITCHEN AND SNOOKER ROOM.MIDDLE FLOOR CONTAINS BEDROOM, SPARE-ROOM AND BATHROOM.TOP FLOOR CONTAINS TWO MORE BEDROOMS. { 3.COTTAGE}(TWO-STOREY), BUILT IN THE {17TH CENTURY}OF{ROUGH CAST SLATE. ORIGINALLY TWO FARM LABOURERS COTTAGES COMBINED IN 20TH CENTURY TO FORM ONE HOUSE.IT CONTAINS 3 BEDROOMS AND A BATHROOM/TOILET,LARGE KITCHEN-DINER, LOUNGE,DINING ROOM.RECENT EXTENSIONS INCLUDE A BEDROOM AND GARAGE.
